[SPEAKER_00] i ja nisam.

760
00:31:40,920 --> 00:31:42,160
[SPEAKER_00] Blago se njima, nama ne.

761
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:47,039
[SPEAKER_00] Svi ćete izaći

762
00:31:47,039 --> 00:31:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] iz ove crkve.

763
00:31:48,299 --> 00:31:49,359
[SPEAKER_00] Blago se njima, nama ne.

764
00:31:49,359 --> 00:31:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] I sad,

765
00:31:51,079 --> 00:31:53,240
[SPEAKER_00] ako mislite da to nije biblijski,

766
00:31:53,240 --> 00:31:54,339
[SPEAKER_00] čitajte psalme.

767
00:31:54,339 --> 00:31:56,200
[SPEAKER_00] U psalmima

768
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] non-stop žalovanje tuga.

769
00:31:58,519 --> 00:32:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] I plakanje nad onime

770
00:32:00,380 --> 00:32:01,640
[SPEAKER_00] šta im je napravljeno,

771
00:32:01,640 --> 00:32:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] šta su doživjeli

772
00:32:02,880 --> 00:32:03,819
[SPEAKER_00] i gdje je bila nepravda.

773
00:32:03,819 --> 00:32:06,319
[SPEAKER_00] Imate čak i knjigu

774
00:32:06,319 --> 00:32:07,099
[SPEAKER_00] u bibliji koja se zovu

775
00:32:07,099 --> 00:32:07,740
[SPEAKER_00] Tuželjke.

776
00:32:07,740 --> 00:32:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, biblijski je taj proces.

777
00:32:10,980 --> 00:32:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da dopustim

778
00:32:12,539 --> 00:32:14,259
[SPEAKER_00] da ovo tu što mislim

779
00:32:14,259 --> 00:32:15,180
[SPEAKER_00] da nisam primio,

780
00:32:15,180 --> 00:32:16,240
[SPEAKER_00] da ga provedem

781
00:32:16,240 --> 00:32:17,039
[SPEAKER_00] kroz taj proces.

782
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ej, stvarno nije bilo pravedno.

783
00:32:19,579 --> 00:32:21,440
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ću to isplakat.

784
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jer sam očekivao

785
00:32:22,420 --> 00:32:22,980
[SPEAKER_00] i nisam dobio.

786
00:32:22,980 --> 00:32:23,839
[SPEAKER_00] I sad ću pustit.

787
00:32:23,839 --> 00:32:24,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

788
00:32:24,539 --> 00:32:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ciprijan,

789
00:32:25,420 --> 00:32:27,839
[SPEAKER_00] gdje mi te dio.

790
00:32:32,839 --> 00:32:36,440
[SPEAKER_00] dopusti si da budeš iscijeljen

791
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] tamo gdje si primio rane.

792
00:32:38,119 --> 00:32:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite, Ciprijan to piše

793
00:32:39,559 --> 00:32:40,839
[SPEAKER_00] od 250. godine.

794
00:32:40,839 --> 00:32:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] Cijela nova moderna psihologija

795
00:32:44,380 --> 00:32:45,220
[SPEAKER_00] priča o tome.

796
00:32:45,220 --> 00:32:47,220
[SPEAKER_00] Odi do tog malog ti

797
00:32:47,220 --> 00:32:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] koji je ranjen,

798
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:48,640
[SPEAKER_00] koji je povređeni

799
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:49,299
[SPEAKER_00] i odi tamo

800
00:32:49,299 --> 00:32:50,619
[SPEAKER_00] da on doživi iscijeljenje,

801
00:32:50,619 --> 00:32:51,299
[SPEAKER_00] da može živjeti.

802
00:32:51,700 --> 00:32:52,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ciprijan je to napisao.

803
00:32:52,799 --> 00:32:54,700
[SPEAKER_00] Dopusti si da budeš iscijeljen

804
00:32:54,700 --> 00:32:56,160
[SPEAKER_00] tamo gdje si primio rane.

805
00:32:56,160 --> 00:32:57,180
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje si primio rane?

806
00:32:57,180 --> 00:32:59,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ne sad kad si možeš objasniti,

807
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:01,279
[SPEAKER_00] nego tad kad si nisi mogao objasniti.

808
00:33:01,279 --> 00:33:03,200
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto tata nema vremena za mene?

809
00:33:03,200 --> 00:33:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto mama mi nije pokazala ljubav?

810
00:33:05,119 --> 00:33:06,859
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je moj brat dobio ovo

811
00:33:06,859 --> 00:33:07,700
[SPEAKER_00] ni ja nisam dobio?

812
00:33:07,700 --> 00:33:09,200
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je moja sestra dobila ono?

813
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:09,759
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto ja nisam?

814
00:33:09,759 --> 00:33:12,279
[SPEAKER_00] U toj, tom trenutku

815
00:33:12,279 --> 00:33:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] postoji rupa

816
00:33:13,940 --> 00:33:15,819
[SPEAKER_00] koja nema iscijeljenje.

817
00:33:15,819 --> 00:33:22,759
[SPEAKER_00] Sve što si u glavi objasnimo,

818
00:33:22,759 --> 00:33:24,779
[SPEAKER_00] možemo si intelektualno objasniti,

819
00:33:24,779 --> 00:33:26,460
[SPEAKER_00] je okej proces.

820
00:33:26,460 --> 00:33:29,079
[SPEAKER_00] I to ćemo si jako brzo objasniti.

821
00:33:29,079 --> 00:33:30,900
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, bila je takva situacija.

822
00:33:30,900 --> 00:33:33,099
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo je to, to i to.

823
00:33:33,099 --> 00:33:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] I u mojoj glavi je savršeno jasno.

824
00:33:36,859 --> 00:33:39,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, ako ne prođemo kroz proces,

825
00:33:39,359 --> 00:33:42,759
[SPEAKER_00] nismo niti doživjeli iscijeljenje.

826
00:33:42,759 --> 00:33:44,779
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je sve posloženo ovdje.

827
00:33:44,779 --> 00:33:46,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo tu,

828
00:33:46,140 --> 00:33:47,819
[SPEAKER_00] ostaje neriješeno.

829
00:33:47,819 --> 00:33:50,940
[SPEAKER_00] Moj unutarnji čovjek nije dobio ono što je trebao.

830
00:33:50,940 --> 00:33:53,960
[SPEAKER_00] A Pavao moli za unutarnjeg čovjeka.

831
00:33:53,960 --> 00:33:55,160
[SPEAKER_00] Poslanice Fežinao,

832
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:56,880
[SPEAKER_00] Pavao moli za unutarnjeg čovjeka.

833
00:33:56,880 --> 00:33:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] To znači da unutarnji čovjek postoji.

834
00:33:58,880 --> 00:34:00,720
[SPEAKER_00] To nije psihološka izmišljotina,

835
00:34:00,720 --> 00:34:02,900
[SPEAKER_00] to nije nešto što sad stavljamo

836
00:34:02,900 --> 00:34:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] u koštac, ne znam s čim.

837
00:34:04,539 --> 00:34:06,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pavao moli za unutarnji čovjeka.

838
00:34:06,640 --> 00:34:08,340
[SPEAKER_00] Unutarnji čovjek treba primiti nešto.

839
00:34:08,340 --> 00:34:11,420
[SPEAKER_00] Znanje, spoznaju, ljubav.

840
00:34:11,420 --> 00:34:14,599
[SPEAKER_00] I treba primiti to iskustvo koje mu fali.

841
00:34:14,599 --> 00:34:15,760
[SPEAKER_00] Treba mu ga dopustiti.

842
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:17,260
[SPEAKER_00] Treba proći kroz to.

843
00:34:28,300 --> 00:34:29,239
[SPEAKER_00] To sam rekao?

844
00:34:29,239 --> 00:34:29,539
[SPEAKER_00] To sam rekao?

845
00:34:29,539 --> 00:34:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, postoje neke razloze zašto smo mi ljubomorni i zavidni.

846
00:34:37,460 --> 00:34:41,179
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto nas nešto triggerira, a zašto nešto ne.

847
00:34:42,219 --> 00:34:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] Nismo svi isti.

848
00:34:43,059 --> 00:34:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ne prolazimo svi iste procese, ne imamo svi iste ranjenosti.

849
00:34:46,059 --> 00:34:49,940
[SPEAKER_00] Možda slične, ali svako ima svoju priču.

850
00:34:49,940 --> 00:34:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] E baš kroz tu svoju priču moraš proći s Bogom.

851
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:57,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ju ignoriraš, onda ćeš gubiti na drugim stvarima nekad nešto.

852
00:34:57,599 --> 00:35:05,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ako nismo dobili intimnost, vrijeme, prisutnost, sigurnost koja mi je bila potrebna,

853
00:35:05,039 --> 00:35:07,099
[SPEAKER_00] ta bol ostaje.

854
00:35:07,099 --> 00:35:13,639
[SPEAKER_00] I onda moram doći do tog korijena gdje je problem počeo i gdje nema dovoljno za mene.

855
00:35:13,639 --> 00:35:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo vas i previše.

856
00:35:16,500 --> 00:35:18,860
[SPEAKER_00] Neko se nije mogao brinuti za sve.

857
00:35:18,860 --> 00:35:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, roditelji su se molali posvetiti nekom drugome.

858
00:35:21,940 --> 00:35:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] Sve pet.

859
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:26,179
[SPEAKER_00] U glavi, ček, opravdano.

860
00:35:26,179 --> 00:35:28,280
[SPEAKER_00] Objasnite o malom djetetu.

861
00:35:28,280 --> 00:35:29,400
[SPEAKER_00] Kako to misliš?

862
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] Imali su vremena za drugi, za mene ne.

863
00:35:31,559 --> 00:35:33,260
[SPEAKER_00] Što mene dovoljno ne voli.

864
00:35:33,260 --> 00:35:38,239
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo je to objasniti o malom djetetu.

865
00:35:38,239 --> 00:35:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ako vam ne doobjašnjavanje toga o malom djetetu,

866
00:35:40,920 --> 00:35:44,760
[SPEAKER_00] znači ni vaše malo djete to nije skužilo šta god si ti smislio sa trenutno u glavi.

867
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:48,820
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ne odmota to i ostavi.

868
00:35:48,820 --> 00:35:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] Tako nego, Bože,

869
00:35:50,440 --> 00:35:52,820
[SPEAKER_00] kopsal misti.

870
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:55,920
[SPEAKER_00] Bože, ovo tu sve je

871
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] jadno,

872
00:35:58,119 --> 00:35:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] tužno,

873
00:35:59,019 --> 00:36:00,739
[SPEAKER_00] žedan sam,

874
00:36:00,739 --> 00:36:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] trebam te,

875
00:36:02,019 --> 00:36:04,179
[SPEAKER_00] trebam pomoć,

876
00:36:04,179 --> 00:36:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] trebam iscijeljenje,

877
00:36:05,500 --> 00:36:08,019
[SPEAKER_00] trebam ljubav,

878
00:36:08,019 --> 00:36:09,900
[SPEAKER_00] trebam tvoju pažnju.

879
00:36:12,239 --> 00:36:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] jer, znate, na kome će se iskaliti ta tvoja potreba?

880
00:36:15,579 --> 00:36:16,639
[SPEAKER_00] Na tvom partneru.

881
00:36:16,639 --> 00:36:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] To ćeš sve tražiti od partnera da je riješi.

882
00:36:19,460 --> 00:36:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] A ne može partnera obnoviti nešto što su nam trebali dati roditelji.

883
00:36:23,460 --> 00:36:27,360
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam prije, ne znam koliko, deseta godina, kad sam pričao na jednom susretu,

884
00:36:28,119 --> 00:36:30,260
[SPEAKER_00] i dolazi mi i kažem ono, čekamo,

885
00:36:30,260 --> 00:36:33,280
[SPEAKER_00] neko može imat 50, 60, 70 godina,

886
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:35,360
[SPEAKER_00] još uvijek čekat potvrdu svog roditelja,

887
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] kojeg nema,

888
00:36:36,079 --> 00:36:37,659
[SPEAKER_00] ali još uvijek ga čeka.

889
00:36:37,659 --> 00:36:40,179
[SPEAKER_00] I dolazi mi na moliku jedna starija žena,

890
00:36:40,179 --> 00:36:42,059
[SPEAKER_00] od 70,

891
00:36:42,059 --> 00:36:44,159
[SPEAKER_00] možda čak i 80 godina,

892
00:36:44,159 --> 00:36:45,300
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže,

893
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] želim da me Bog ozdravi,

894
00:36:48,860 --> 00:36:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] jer još uvijek čekam pohvala od svog oca.

895
00:36:54,039 --> 00:36:55,440
[SPEAKER_00] 70 i nešto godina.

896
00:36:55,440 --> 00:36:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] I dalje ne živi svoju slobodu,

897
00:36:58,880 --> 00:37:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] i dalje ne živi ono,

898
00:37:00,119 --> 00:37:01,139
[SPEAKER_00] jer ona sa 70,

899
00:37:01,139 --> 00:37:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] oca kojeg nema,

900
00:37:02,079 --> 00:37:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] još uvijek čeka njegov pohvalu.

901
00:37:04,460 --> 00:37:08,320
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je skužila,

902
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:10,159
[SPEAKER_00] ne treba mi zdravlje,

903
00:37:10,159 --> 00:37:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] ne treba mi ništa,

904
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:13,179
[SPEAKER_00] ali treba mi to da to pustim,

905
00:37:13,179 --> 00:37:14,820
[SPEAKER_00] jer to još uvijek ne mogu pustiti.

906
00:37:14,820 --> 00:37:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] I možda smo trenutno zabavljeni

907
00:37:19,519 --> 00:37:21,199
[SPEAKER_00] sa svim mogućim stvarima o svom životu,

908
00:37:21,199 --> 00:37:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] pa nismo ni svjesni svega toga šta se prolazi u nama,

909
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali šta se događa kada si sam?

910
00:37:25,380 --> 00:37:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] Spavam.

911
00:37:27,880 --> 00:37:30,719
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je isto problem.

912
00:37:30,719 --> 00:37:33,400
[SPEAKER_00] Od čega bježiš dok spavaš?

913
00:37:33,400 --> 00:37:34,360
[SPEAKER_00] Od umora.

914
00:37:34,360 --> 00:37:39,039
[SPEAKER_00] Šta se događa kad si soćim sam sa sobom?

915
00:37:39,039 --> 00:37:41,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sve utihne?

916
00:37:41,900 --> 00:37:43,780
[SPEAKER_00] Na, na, na, na.

917
00:37:43,780 --> 00:37:47,099
[SPEAKER_00] I teško mi je.

918
00:37:47,099 --> 00:37:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] Teško mi je onda s mojim mislima.

919
00:37:48,440 --> 00:37:50,719
[SPEAKER_00] Teško mi je onda sam sa sobom.

920
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] Šta se događa kada nikog nema?

921
00:37:56,199 --> 00:38:00,260
[SPEAKER_00] Da mi se sve stavim sa strane, ono mučim se s tim stvarima,

922
00:38:00,260 --> 00:38:01,599
[SPEAKER_00] da sve ugasim, da se maknem,

923
00:38:01,599 --> 00:38:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] kad prolazim kroz loše emocije,

924
00:38:03,460 --> 00:38:05,059
[SPEAKER_00] onda samo daj mi nekog sadržanja,

925
00:38:05,059 --> 00:38:07,760
[SPEAKER_00] daj nešto da me zabavi, da trenutno to ignoriram.

926
00:38:09,440 --> 00:38:11,519
[SPEAKER_00] I sve to samo ja radim, nikog od vas ne.

927
00:38:11,519 --> 00:38:15,239
[SPEAKER_00] Skužim,

928
00:38:15,239 --> 00:38:17,480
[SPEAKER_00] daj mi samo nešto da me zabavlja,

929
00:38:17,480 --> 00:38:18,900
[SPEAKER_00] jer trenutno se ne mogu nositi s ovem.

930
00:38:18,900 --> 00:38:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] Uopće to ne mogu vidjeti,

931
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu to održiti, ne mogu se uočiti.

932
00:38:22,500 --> 00:38:24,679
[SPEAKER_00] I onda trebam nešto što će me zabaviti,

933
00:38:24,679 --> 00:38:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] tako da ne mislim o tome.

934
00:38:25,880 --> 00:38:26,820
[SPEAKER_00] I onda si mislim,

935
00:38:26,820 --> 00:38:28,519
[SPEAKER_00] nema me.

936
00:38:30,579 --> 00:38:32,840
[SPEAKER_00] Sad me sigurno nitko od vas ne vidi,

937
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:35,320
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam ja pokriju svoje oči

938
00:38:35,320 --> 00:38:37,840
[SPEAKER_00] i ne vidite me.

939
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:40,199
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite koliko je to naivno.

940
00:38:40,199 --> 00:38:42,920
[SPEAKER_00] To je kad se zabavimo sa svim drugim stvarima,

941
00:38:42,920 --> 00:38:44,579
[SPEAKER_00] nismo riješili ovu hrpu.

942
00:38:44,579 --> 00:38:46,480
[SPEAKER_00] Veša,

943
00:38:46,480 --> 00:38:48,079
[SPEAKER_00] koja stoji sa strane,

944
00:38:48,079 --> 00:38:49,420
[SPEAKER_00] kao,

945
00:38:49,420 --> 00:38:51,019
[SPEAKER_00] sad je nema.

946
00:38:51,019 --> 00:38:54,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ne vidim tu hrpu, nema je.

947
00:38:54,199 --> 00:38:56,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, to tu stoji i čeka.

948
00:38:56,179 --> 00:38:58,239
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ćemo mi to riješiti.

949
00:38:58,239 --> 00:38:59,239
[SPEAKER_00] Adam i Eva,

950
00:39:00,280 --> 00:39:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] nema dovoljno za sve.

951
00:39:01,500 --> 00:39:03,719
[SPEAKER_00] Kad su Adam i Eva povjerovali u tu laž,

952
00:39:03,719 --> 00:39:04,739
[SPEAKER_00] kad im je zmija došla,

953
00:39:04,739 --> 00:39:05,219
[SPEAKER_00] je rekla mi je,

954
00:39:05,219 --> 00:39:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] je li on stvarno to Bog rekao?

955
00:39:07,619 --> 00:39:11,139
[SPEAKER_00] Pa zato što on zna da niste dobili najbolje što može.

956
00:39:11,139 --> 00:39:13,179
[SPEAKER_00] Možete kad pojedete s tog ploda,

957
00:39:13,179 --> 00:39:15,159
[SPEAKER_00] kad pojedete plod s tog stabla,

958
00:39:15,159 --> 00:39:16,340
